Flaherty Says the ‘Volatility’ of Canadian Dollar a Concern

-- B y   A n d r e w   M a y e d a
-- 
2011-10-04T13:00:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/flaherty-says-the-volatility-of-canadian-dollar-a-concern.html
Canadian Finance Minister  Jim
Flaherty  said the “volatility” of the country’s currency is a
concern.  Speaking to reporters in Ottawa, Flaherty also said
European countries need to take steps that “overwhelm” their
debt crisis and get ahead of the market.  To contact the reporter on this story:
